OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe cool
OL,6,Fbreeze as well as showers will ease
OL,7,Fovernight, and it will become mostly
OL,8,Fdry by morning. Some clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping under lighter winds,
OL,10,Fallowing for a chilly end to the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FThe odd early shower is
OL,13,Fpossible, otherwise a dry day with
OL,14,Flight winds. Cloudy at times, but with
OL,15,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,16,Fless chilly in the lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
