OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with light winds on Saturday. Some
OL,7,Fshowers possible on Sunday. Gradually
OL,8,Fturning wet from the west on Monday.
OL,9,FTemperatures returning to near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
